  "message": "chore: update .gitignore to allow runtime workload corpus and update wavefront pipeline artifact\n\n- .gitignore: refine artifacts/ rules to explicitly allow\n  runtime_workload_corpus_v*.json files while keeping the rest of\n  artifacts/ ignored. Uses negation pattern (!artifacts/) to re-include\n  the directory, then artifacts/* to ignore contents, then\n  !artifacts/runtime_workload_corpus_v*.json to whitelist the corpus.\n- Update raptorq_track_f_wavefront_pipeline_v1.json with latest\n  benchmark data (54 insertions, 54 deletions \u2014 field value updates)\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
